{"tid":34556,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"[集思廣益] 可能係第一首LIHKG嘅原創歌","createTime":"2016-12-11T13:58:22.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-21T05:37:35.000Z","uid":24754,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9a95d2ec6bff6b00a1e4987535f6957ec500c88c","tid":34556,"uid":24754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T13:58:22.000Z","msg":"是咁的！細佬我寫左首歌想請各位巴絲填詞，共同創作一首歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實呢首歌喺之前寫落，𠴱時有人填好詞，但係可惜屋企嘅equipment 壞左，冇辦法錄音。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而且Final Exam就嚟到，所以就放低咗。<br />\n依家設備冇哂問題，除時可以錄得，但可以已經搵唔翻填嘅朋友問佢credit<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以我決定重新填詞，之前高登仔嘅填詞功力人人都知道係冇得彈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以我希望你哋可以一齊集思廣益完全首歌 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n呢首歌寫出嚟個感覺喺開頭有少少唔開心，跟住慢慢recover翻。<br />\n唔知大家嘅感覺一唔一樣呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n另外本來個Melody應該填普通話比較適合，但我希望大家可以填粵語，本土啲嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n聽歌LINK:<br />\n<a href=\"https://soundcloud.com/user-150630877/20161211a\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsoundcloud.com%2Fuser-150630877%2F20161211a&d=oyvWpG%2BWImCkRdXppRAciwv3KisNQlPySkJrDkY9tT8%3D&h=374b2d0a\" target=\"_blank\">https://soundcloud.com/user-150630877/20161211a</a>"},{"pid":"d9c4e19e4639a461ed921a4205051c230fc6ee71","tid":34556,"uid":9131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T14:01:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 留名"},{"pid":"60c43f200f1536f172d23b17cac780574aeffe4c","tid":34556,"uid":24754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T14:08:13.000Z","msg":"<bloc